      <title>Treyz：投资者的交易就像明天的选举一样</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-27/investors-trading-like-election-is-tomorrow-treyz-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Veda Partners 经济政策研究总监 Henrietta Treyz 表示，投资者对 2024 年总统选举的兴奋几乎达到了狂热的程度。她在“彭博监视”节目中。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-27/investors-trading-like-election-is-tomorrow-treyz-video</guid>
